# Software Requirements Specification

- The system shall provide hierarchical category navigation for construction materials
- The system shall support multiple filtering options (brand, price range, quality parameters) which is dependent on material categoty
- The system shall implement advanced search functionality with autocomplete
- The system shall provide a persistent shopping cart ("bucket") that stays with users while browsing
- The system shall allow side-by-side comparison
- Comparison shall include:
  - Technical specifications in a tabular format
  - Price comparison across vendors
  - Quality ratings and certifications
  - Delivery timeframes
  - Warranty information
- The system shall highlight differences between compared products
- The system shall generate PDF comparison reports for download
- The system shall support English and Hindi interfaces